quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  34,46,Qul 'Innamā 'A`ižukum Biwāĥidatin 'An Taqūmū Lillāhi Mathná Wa Furādá Thumma Tatafakkarū Mā Bişāĥibikum Min Jinnatin 'In Huwa 'Illā Nadhīrun Lakum Bayna Yaday `Adhābin Shadīdin
  34,47,Qul Mā Sa'altukum Min 'Ajrin Fahuwa Lakum 'In 'Ajriya 'Illā `Alá Allāhi Wa Huwa `Alá Kulli Shay'in Shahīdun
  34,48,Qul 'Inna Rabbī Yaqdhifu Bil-Ĥaqqi `Allāmu Al-Ghuyūbi
  34,49,Qul Jā'a Al-Ĥaqqu Wa Mā Yubdi'u Al-Bāţilu Wa Mā Yu`īdu
  34,50,Qul 'In Đalaltu Fa'innamā 'Ađillu `Alá Nafsī Wa 'Ini Ahtadaytu Fabimā Yūĥī 'Ilayya Rabbī 'Innahu Samī`un Qarībun
  34,51,Wa Law Tará 'Idh Fazi`ū Falā Fawta Wa 'Ukhidhū Min Makānin Qarībin
  34,52,Wa Qālū 'Āmannā Bihi Wa 'Anná Lahumu At-Tanāwushu Min Makānin Ba`īdin
  34,53,Wa Qad Kafarū Bihi Min Qablu Wa Yaqdhifūna Bil-Ghaybi Min Makānin Ba`īdin
  34,54,Wa Ĥīla Baynahum Wa Bayna Mā Yashtahūna Kamā Fu`ila Bi'ashyā`ihim Min Qablu 'Innahum Kānū Fī Shakkin Murībin